  <h2>V0.7 GA highlights</h2>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Post-quantum signatures</strong> — Dilithium5 (NIST FIPS 204), <code>@pq_signed</code></li>
    <li><strong>FHE</strong> — <code>encrypted&lt;T&gt;</code>, <code>fhe_add</code>, <code>fhe_mul</code>, ERC-8227 compliant</li>
    <li><strong>ZK proofs</strong> — <code>zk_prove</code> / <code>zk_verify</code>, Nova IVC + Halo2, ERC-8229</li>
    <li><strong>Cryptographic amnesia</strong> — <code>amnesia {{ }}</code> blocks, ERC-8228 ceremony lifecycle</li>
    <li><strong>Multi-target</strong> — EVM, Aster Chain (ID 1996), WASM (experimental)</li>
    <li><strong>LSP</strong> — 38+ lint detectors in VS Code, Neovim, IntelliJ</li>
    <li><strong>OMEGA V4 audited</strong> — 41 findings, 5 Critical, all resolved</li>
  </ul>
